{"tid":544282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩住樂富/黃大仙既巴打絲打入一入黎","createTime":"2018-01-29T11:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T11:46:55.000Z","uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc1b208f8a87ddf5519ad8ac4e0eacfa4e6e7c6","tid":544282,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"我朋友係琴日隻貓女走失左，如果你地係住果頭，希望你地行過既時候可以留意下，麻煩晒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貓女 Coco 於2018年1月27日上午破壞了窗邊索帶，然後於十樓墮下。地點為九龍黃大仙天馬苑迴旋處。當值保安稱見到Coco走路時「拐下拐下」，現在牠受傷了但未能尋獲令人十分擔心，因為Coco是長期病患。如果有善心人已接走了牠或者曾經見過牠蹤影請儘快聯絡，重酬。希望貓貓能吉貓天相！感激不盡！<br />\n<br />\n貓貓 Coco特徵：<br />\n一歲 / 女仔雌性 / 灰色虎紋 / 長尾<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法：<br />\n手提 60308334<br />\ntelegram<a href=\"https://t.me/manwestbbg_pure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmanwestbbg_pure&d=2XY%2FVxP1g9%2F6Fp5D5MFSFE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=20c153b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/manwestbbg_pure</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒你地 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/191115_d60c07c602bb312f5f3866a6bd158eba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F191115_d60c07c602bb312f5f3866a6bd158eba.png&h=cafab089&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/191127_b377e9644c1222a846be2b0bd0d4ccf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F191127_b377e9644c1222a846be2b0bd0d4ccf7.png&h=b2e84901&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88ac14c5bffadc6bf132a094ea83604fa7996687","tid":544282,"uid":105066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"幫你留意下 祝早日巡回coco"},{"pid":"7a309a2720c3f49de3e2be6eb8fdd580cae8164a","tid":544282,"uid":105066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ac14c5bffadc6bf132a094ea83604